    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/5dc06f409a90c388fbbd04d3a061dbf8.webp?t=1743777679\" width=62 height=64 /></span> 早上好！我是PAI —— 你的个人AI助手，很高兴为你服务！<br><br>很抱歉提前唤醒你，但世界早已迎来末日，<strong>而你却在沉睡中错过了一切！</strong><br><br>不过别担心，我会全力协助你的！有了我和你可靠的原型战衣，<strong>你可以开采矿石、建造地下基地，在这里生存下去!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/7f32c3f5e70a2a4a17472926bdcab9a8.poster.avif?t=1743777679\" width=509 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/7f32c3f5e70a2a4a17472926bdcab9a8.webm?t=1743777679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>虽然这里没有阳光，但你不是独自一个人。我已经找到了一些其他幸存者，你可以<strong>唤醒他们，并将他们带回你新建的基地！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/3c6ad724074d35d454832eed4bc281cb.poster.avif?t=1743777679\" width=509 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/3c6ad724074d35d454832eed4bc281cb.webm?t=1743777679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>不过，如果你想要重返地表，仅仅生存下去还远远不够。你需要：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拓展并建设一个自动化的基地……</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/bbfe617e578afc6af6659416a2f35f08.poster.avif?t=1743777679\" width=509 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/bbfe617e578afc6af6659416a2f35f08.webm?t=1743777679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >向熟悉的面孔求助……</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/3765ec82b5d28288c7b07519093d9bf1.poster.avif?t=1743777679\" width=509 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/3765ec82b5d28288c7b07519093d9bf1.webm?t=1743777679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>再者，不是我想吓你，但我<strong>探测到了一些绝非地球的怪物！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/f23b2088201210c7b379b62142fa8f86.poster.avif?t=1743777679\" width=509 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/f23b2088201210c7b379b62142fa8f86.webm?t=1743777679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>虽然我不是专门为世界末日场景而编程的，但有我在，<strong>再加上你的帮助</strong>，我相信人类一定能渡过这个难关！<br><br><strong>《Aground Zero》是我们前作《Aground》的3D衍生作品，故事发生在原作的同一时间线内。即使没玩过《Aground》也能轻松上手！</strong><br><br><strong>注意：</strong>本地合作模式中，仅一名玩家可使用键盘和鼠标。 其他玩家（最多支持4人）需使用单独的手柄（当然，玩家们也可以都使用手柄进行游戏）。",
